{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, they're covered in snow, with their bodies-- I can-- I can imagine what-- they could-- he was just two meters over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was in the open high wagon without covers, so he could see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You could look in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was going over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the girl was eating a chocolate bar, or some candy bar anyhow, you know, not chocolate, but imitation chocolate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the boys was sipping strawberry juice, strawberry or lemonade or something like this, strawberry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he was sipping it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I and a couple others started to beg for him to give us something to drink, water or give us a drink.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he-- he let the almost full strawberry bottle go, and I caught it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I caught the bottle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, he was just-- he bent down and let it drop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I caught the bottle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And like mad I started to drink the sugar, you know, sugar in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I was drinking like mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And by that time, two or three other men who were still in reasonably good condition see what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they quickly jumped on me and took the-- took the bottle from me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I had about 20 seconds head start.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "By that time I drank as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then they finished the bottle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyway, that-- that's all I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then the train went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And one of my friends went completely crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "His ulcer perforated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "His stomach was open, with blood running everywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there was more and more dead people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Anyhow, eventually the train arrived to the station, which was cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We read it out, Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It meant nothing for us, just a German name, Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the fresh group of 50 SS men, just must have finished their breakfast.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
